data.value: Automatically configure the receiver attached to the selected port to output correction messages.

data.name: label22.Text
data.value:
At connect the receiver will start a “survey-in” to determine the GPS precision location. The survey-in is finished when the RTCM Base location is no longer changing. Based on the location and signal it could take a couple minutes
Once the survey is completed, you are ready to go.
